Cilvia Demo is the debut extended play (EP) by American hip hop recording artist Isaiah Rashad, released on January 28, 2014, under Top Dawg Entertainment. The EP features guest appearances from Jean Deaux and Michael Da Vinci, as well as his Top Dawg label-mates SZA, Schoolboy Q and Jay Rock. The EP's production was handled by several record producers, namely Ross Vega, Mr. Carmack, Joseph Stranger, Black Metaphor, TheFarhot, Chris Calor, D. Sanders and Digi+Phonics producer Sounwave.
